imgur-screenshot (Imgur Screenshot Uploader)

imgur-screenshot is the Imgur Screenshot Uploader for Linux & OS X
from imgur.com/tools.

Features:

  * Upload screenshot or image files
  * Copy link to clipboard
  * Customizable configuration
  * Edit image before uploading
  * Upload anonymously or to an account
  * Create and add to albums
  * Filename, link, and deletion link history is stored
  * Automatic image deletion
  * Update notifications

Just set your screenshot folder in imgur-screenshot script.
